Package Utils

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArgumentReader
    Class that manages the initial argument handling from the jar being called.
    CSV_Builder
    A class that allows you to easily format different strung values into a CSV
    CSV_Builder_Objects
    A class that holds a series of objects for formatting purposes within the CSV_Builder implementation Overriding the toString() method of an object will override how a CSV_Builder will print
    CSV_Builder_Objects.CSV_Double
    Nested class to help correctly format doubles for CSVs
    CSV_Builder_Objects.CSV_Percent  
    FileSystem
    Class to manage custom functions related to interacting with the FileSystem
    HardCode
    A class for the sole purpose of including most of the global hard-coded values in Additionally, it does include some functions
    JobTracker
    Class to track the timing of events throughout the program Note: A job must be finished before another job is added on
